        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The mean period of ITU stay was 448 h (SD 749.2), median 184 h (IQR374). On Spearman's rank correlation, this was also not related to the weight ratio (p = −0.04, p = 0.58) (Fig. 5). Again, if the six patients who were in the ITU for more than 2000 h were excluded, there was still no association (p <0.01, p = 0.98).",
